#Requirement

1. I should get the parking spot for my car if available, if it is not avaolable I will be denied
2. There could be different size of car - small, medium, large
3. Parking lot has different floors
4. My parking spot should be nearest to the exit gate
5. For each parking there would be a parking ticket that has parking charge, parking spot, parking time, due time etc.
6. Fine is applicable if parked after due time
7. Utilize the space
8. Should be aware of which parking spot is vacant or filled


